Powers.DescLong: A very quick, but low damage attack that lowers your target's attack and movement speed. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Very Fast

Gravitic Emanation sends bolts of dark Nictus energy to multiple targets within a cone area in front of the caster.  Gravitic Emanation deals moderate Negative Energy damage and leave foes with reduced attack and movement speed. Damage: Moderate Recharge: Slow

A much more powerful, yet slower version of Shadow Bolt. Shadow Blast sends focused negative Nictus energy at a foe.  This attack can knock down foes and will leave the target's attack and movement speed slowed. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Moderate
